The Beatles - Live at the BBC (2CD) [1994]
released Nov 30 1994
MONO

Re-upload with complete art work and updated tags

PLEASE NOTE!
Normally I rip with EAC to flac files. But here I had to use Winamp for
CD 1. For some reason EAC couldn't read CD 1. I've enclosed log files from
Audiochecker to verify that the tracks are genuine flac files. CD 2 is
ripped with EAC to flac.
